                            <comment id="12897370" author="kzhang" created="Wed, 11 Aug 2010 18:28:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;TestBlockToken fails  (&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HDFS-1284&quot; title=&quot;TestBlockToken fails&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HDFS-1284&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HDFS-1284&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) on some platforms because of this. Before the test starts, it tries to initialize UGI using a customized conf with property &quot;hadoop.security.authentication&quot; set to &quot;kerberos&quot;. However, because of this bug, the value eventually been used is &quot;simple&quot; from the default conf. And the test fails as a result.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
